# Review checklist

Before finalizing, verify:
- Sync options work.
- Async options work.
- Debouncing works.
- Previous async requests are cancelled.
- Out-of-order responses cannot overwrite current results.
- Keyboard navigation works from closed and open states.
- Enter selects.
- Escape closes.
- Click outside closes.
- Empty, loading, and error states are visible.
- README explains API, architecture, AI workflow, and tradeoffs.
